     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'
     ELSE "EKPO"."LOEKZ"
END

components.dropdownText: ABC Filter for Vendor on Net Value

formula.text: AVG(CASE WHEN KPI("CT Subprocess") < <%= targetCT %> THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END)

sheetFilter.text:
<% if(low_CT != "") { %>
FILTER 
    <%=unit%>_BETWEEN(
        PU_FIRST("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = '<%= start_activity %>' ),
        PU_LAST ("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = '<%= end_activity  %>')
    )  > <%= low_CT %>;
<% } %>
